<i>10,000 feet above Lincoln Park.</i>

00:25.159 --> 00:27.559
<i>It doesn't reach the ground
for 45 minutes.</i>

00:31.032 --> 00:35.100
<i>At 1:58, the snowflake lands
on the cheek of Edith Struit.</i>

